'''[[scramble]]d [[egg]]s'''
#A [[dish]] made by [[beating]] and [[frying]] eggs, sometimes mixed with [[milk]].

====Usage note====
*Although ther plural form is most often used generically for the dish it is perfectly correct to use the singular when only one egg is used.

